	heroEyebrow={`A Father For`}
	heroSubhead={`The empty chair. The silent house. The half of the bed no one will fill again. If you have lost your spouse, you are carrying a grief few words can reach — and there is a Father in heaven who has not looked away. He calls Himself the protector of the widow, and that promise is for you.`}
	heroBase={`https://cdn.sanity.io/images/rusi1hyi/production/e6cfbdce300971f2c17438d108dee155b04d8d5b-1100x733.jpg`}
