	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father, not a rulebook`, bodyHtml: `Grief doesn't need more rules — it needs a Father. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> and defender of the widow wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/psalms/68" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Psalm 68</a> on. So in your loss you meet the One who stands up for you, not one more voice telling you how you should be coping.` },
		{ heading: `It's free, on your phone, with audio for the lonely hours`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — so when sleep won't come or the evening stretches long and silent, you can let His Word be read over you, like a voice in the quiet house.` },
		{ heading: `It speaks to grief, not around it`, bodyHtml: `When the words won't come, start with our <a href="/verses/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">verses by topic</a> for comfort and grief, or learn to bring your sorrow to Him with our <a href="/guides/how-to-pray/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">how-to-pray guide</a> — the Word meets you exactly where the ache is.` },
